WEBVTT

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:32.976
that there really are some benefits
to medical marijuana.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:36.736
Those benefits may not be
as huge or as stunning

00:02:36.760 --> 00:02:39.696
as some of the most avid proponents
of medical marijuana

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:40.936
would have us believe,

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:42.240
but they are real.

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:44.336
Surprise number two:

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:47.056
medical marijuana does have some risks.

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:50.096
Those risks may not be
as huge and as scary

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:53.456
as some of the opponents of medical
marijuana would have us believe,

00:02:53.480 --> 00:02:55.880
but they are real risks, nonetheless.

00:02:56.440 --> 00:02:58.896
But it was the third surprise
that was most ...

00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:00.376
surprising.